## Development

FORGE was built through close collaboration between a human and **Claude** (Anthropic). Architecture decisions, feature planning, and iterative code review were worked through together across many sessions. No code was accepted blindly — every version was analyzed, tested, and refined before inclusion.

The human contribution: product vision, architectural direction, prioritization of what to fix and what to defer, final decisions on every tradeoff.

The AI contribution: implementation, bug detection (including finding its own bugs across versions), and alternative approaches.

This README acknowledges that process honestly. AI-assisted development is increasingly common; what matters is whether the result is correct, understandable, and maintainable. The extensive review history that produced this codebase is evidence of that process.

